title: Immediate Move In For 1 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHK/NJQO', 'At Highland on the Park Apartments, you will find your perfect new home with a unique architectural design.', 'We have many different floor plans to choose from featuring curved bays, angled walls, islands, and peninsulas.', 'You will enjoy the community room, fitness center, and outdoor pool.', 'Highland on the Park has controlled entry, professional on-site management and maintenance.', 'Cats and dogs are welcome.', 'Fiber-optic internet is service available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Highland on the Park home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Walk-in closet', 'Window coverings', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Ceiling fan', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Elevator access', 'Trash chutes', 'Laundry facility', 'Additional storage', 'Fitness center', 'Outdoor swimming pool', 'Sauna', 'Party room', 'Off street parking', 'BBQ & picnic area', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Car wash station', 'Package receiving', 'Highland on the Park Apartments Information', 'Address:', '2000 W. 7th St, St Paul MN, 55116', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=11', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 200', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '8:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '10:00AM - 4:00PM', 'Sunday:', '11:00AM - 3:00PM']
